🔧 Copilot Chatbot Embed — Quick Lesson Guide
🎯 Goal:
Embed + customize your chat widget

Learn iframe basics

Add simple JavaScript interactivity

🧪 Activity 1: Style Your Chat Bubble
📍 File: <style>, class .chat-btn

🔁 Change button color

🔠 Change font size

⭕ Make it a round bubble (try width = height + border-radius: 50%)

🖋 Change text: Open Chatbot → Chat with us!

🧪 Activity 2: Control the Popup
📍 File: <script>, function openChatbot()

✅ Add new function closeChatbot()

🔘 Add a Close button inside .chat-modal

🎯 Task: Make Close button hide the chat

🧪 Activity 3: Explore the iframe
📍 File: <iframe> inside .chat-modal

🪄 Change size (width/height)

🌐 Try replacing the src with another URL (like https://example.com)

🛑 Remove allow="microphone; camera" — what happens?

📱 Add scrolling="yes" and test on mobile

🧪 Bonus: Responsive Design
📍 File: <style>

🧩 Add a media query

css
Copy
Edit
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .chat-modal iframe {
    width: 90%;
    height: 500px;
  }
}
✅ Test on small screen

🧪 Bonus: Escape Key to Close
js
Copy
Edit
document.addEventListener("keydown", (e) => {
  if (e.key === "Escape") closeChatbot();
});
✅ Wrap-Up Checklist

 Custom button designed

 Open/Close chatbot working

 iframe explored

 Modal looks good on mobile